President Muhammadu Buhari on Friday met with security chiefs at the Presidential Villa Abuja. Present at the meeting were Inspector General of Police, Mohammed Adamu, Chief of the Air Staff, Air Marshal Sadique Abubakar;,Chief of Naval Staff, Vice Admiral Ibok Ekwe-Ibas; Chief of Army Staff, Lt.-Gen Tukur Buratai; Chief of Defence Staff, Gen Gabriel Olonisakin; Minister of Defence, Bashir Magash among others 